法規內容.條文內容:
A business name shall not contain the following characters:
1.committee, bureau, department, administration, party, team, center, county (city) government, farmers’ association, fishermen’s association, trade association, industrial union, institution, joint society, welfare society, cooperative, educational association, symposium, seminar, production or sales class, research institute, firm, social association, social club, mutual assistance association, service station, university, college, cultural relics gallery, community, temple, fund, association, judicial person of corporation or foundation, or any other name which may mislead the public into believing that the business has any connection with the government or a public welfare organization;
2.characters which would be in violation of public order or good morals;
3.corporation, trading company, company or any other characters similar to company;
4.affiliate, business relations, relationship, group, alliance, franchise, or any other characters indicating joint business operation.
5.any other inappropriate characters.

A Reservation Application shall be denied if the business scope of a business satisfies one of the following circumstances:
1.would be in violation of public order or good morals;
2.could be operated only by specific professional(s) or technical　　　　　 personnel;
3.is not a business operated by any profit-seeking enterprise;
4.is allowed to be operated only by the government in accordance with the law; or
5.would fulfill any conditions prescribed under other laws or regulations.
